1. What did you do in 2009 that you'd never done before?
ummm quite a few things i suppose :D...i lost a lil bit of weight lmao!!! ;p

2. Did you keep your new years' resolutions, and will you make more for next year?
well i'm still fat, so no, not quite o.O 
i deffo intend 2 make more effort....as i <3 the gym i feel it shud b a bit easier ;p

not 100% sure yet, but either at the hobgoblin or at sum1s house or sumtin...either way as long as i got my click around me i don't care where i am :D

ummm...no o.O

i visited portugal :D

6. What would you like to have in 2010 that you lacked in 2009?
a job lolz ;p

the weekend of the 31st of October n the 1st of November.....best halloween ever, followed by billie joe the next day....nuffin cud b better than that ^_^

i think Myles is my biggest achievement :D sooo proud of that kiddie ^_^ miss him lots >.<

still being fat n not having a job o.O

umm maybe mental illness o.O

my boots r AWESOME!!! ^_^ any clothes/shoes/accessories i've bought this yr r most definatly brilliant ;p

umm on booze n clothing ;p

13. What song will always remind you of 2009?
paparazzi <3 or poker face...MAMAMAMA!!!! ;p

more of the gym for sure ;p more having fun as well

15. What do you wish you'd done less of?
caring o.O getting upset by the actions of others coz they really don't care if they hurt u, need 2 remember 2 care less next yr >.<

16. What was your favourite TV program?
GOSSIP GIRL!!!! :D <3

17. Do you hate anyone now that you didn't hate this time last year?
ummm....nah...same hate list i suppose ;p

18. What was the best book you read?
ummm...i'm not sure i read a book this yr :s that makes me sound very uneducated i kno :s i suppose i read the gruffalo many a time this yr and i luv it soo much ^_^

19. What was your greatest musical discovery?
LADY GAGA!!!!! ^_^ ...and i have been intorduced 2 family force 5 and cash cash who r both pretty gd stuff :p

20. What was your favorite film of this year?
the september issue :D

21. What did you do on your birthday?
i had a pub crawl round camden n we all wore wigs :D...sept most ducked out by the time we got 2 the 2nd bar 4 various reasons o.O...but regardless of these ppl i had a gd time as always at the hobgoblin with the remaining party ppl :D

22. What kept you sane?
umm...i had many an insane moment...not a very happy yr 4 me i think >.< the friends who were there 4 me r wot kept me sane :D

23. Who did you miss?
sangita and nina >.< both r away n i hardly see them >.<
i miss my old bff as well o.O shes mia :s

24. Who was the best new person you met?
i didn;t meet many new ppl this yr...thou i did meet tarry at camp, shes jokes :D

25. Tell us a valuable life lesson you learned in 2009:
people=shit o.O
i suppose, for whatever reason, ppl change....and its sumtimes not for the better
...oh, and i kno NEVER to treat ppl badly, or like they're disposable....coz when the shit hits the fan i wanna kno they i've got ppl there for me...and they won't b if i treat them like crap o.O

...well theres a cheery note to finish on i suppose :D...i still wanna go out o.O....i still need the new lady gaga cd....fame monster ^_^ i am a lil monster :D...also i'm gonna make headbands my thing this yr ;p totally luving them...blair with a candy twist ;p

had a super fabulous day out in ldn town :D
went 2 have lunch with nicky and john from cornwall with my ma n ned (who has been in a stupid mood all day i may add n shud snap outta it n stop being so up her own fat arse! ¬.¬) had a totally inadequet cheese sandwich....eeew >.<
then went round the southbank with my ma for a few hrs coz ned went home....went 2 the tate modern....i hate modern art it is totally SHIT!!! ;p
i even wrote that on a postcard that the tate modern is shit n posted it 2 them :D
walked 2 selfridges 2 meet mona....must tell u bout the AMAZING salad i had :D
they've opened a new food stall in the food hall in selfridges n its called chop'd n its a salad bar n u can ether go with a salad combo they've got already or make ur own...so made a buuuuuf salad :p i had lettuce, roasted peppers, olives and chickpeas with avacado salsa, tortila chips and yougart n mint sauce.....OMGC IT WAS SOOOO BUFF!!! ^_^
totally recomend every1 goes there rite now n trys their own salad :p
so i met mona joon in selfridges coz i had won tickets 2 the icecreamists launch party ^_^
went down 2 where it was in the shop...turn up n say we r on the guest list..oh of course lemmie find ur names....no ur not there ¬.¬
i was like but i won tickets on facebook n the woman e-mailed me 2 say our names were on the list >.<...i believe u come on in n heres a coupon for free icecream :D WOOT!!!! ^_^
so me n mona had nuts about chocland yard....which isbasically like nutella but an icecream n not at all sickly....the dude won't take our vouchers so i tell another lady bout it n she says course those vouchers r 4 free icecream...so we desided 2 pay 4 that scoop n get another one free....brown bread icecream omcg buuuuuuuuuuufff!!!!!! ;p
there was a band playing as well...they played loadz of prince songs which was kl n made mona v happy...after we took pics of the place coz it was all pink n black n awesome...then we went 2 look round the rest of selfridges coz i've never done that b4
headed straight 4 the designer clothes section :D...touched real vivien westwood ^_^ touched real marc by marc jacobs ^_^ touched real christian loubution shoes ^_^...a very happy nite for me :D :D :D :D

went 2 the high street section in selfridges n they were doing promotions for a new fashion website called fashionair (sounds like an airline i kno o.O) and they had a free photo booth...wot happens is u get video recorded 4 30secs n then they take pics of u..so me n mona did it 2ce so we had a pic each..it was very fun...then they started filming this random girl asking her about her outfit....i almost had an amanda moment ;p....very tempted 2 push her out of the way shouting OUTTA MY WAY SKANK n then start posing 2 the camera ;p...resisted thankfully coz it wudda ended badly o.O

after lookin at all the stuff we desided 2 leave so we walked 2wards the bus stop...noticed m&s was still open at 9:30pm so we went 2 have a look....they were having the big fashion nite out party ( to do with ldn fashion week it seems) :D so we stayed n i drank a bunch of free champagne which is always gd...filmed a few pieces 4 keeping up with candy n joon....drank more free champagne watched a fashion workshop n danced around n then left :D

all n all it was an AWESOME fashionista's evening out ^_^ can't wait 2 b featured in ppl like them in style magazine lolz....as if ;p

sooo.....lets see how far positive thinking can get me ;p...its hard coz i've never been one to think of the bright side...but lets give it a go
